<h1>About THE Program</h1>
<p>The Trail Area Health &amp; Environment Program is a comprehensive, community-led program with 5 main areas of activity: Family Health, Home &amp; Garden, Air Quality, Parks and Wildlands, and Property Development. Our mission is to promote people&rsquo;s health and environment, with a focus on preventing children&rsquo;s exposure to lead. &nbsp;</p>
<p>The <a title="Air Quality Fact sheet" href="/pages/airquality">Air Quality Program</a> reduces smelter emissions and makes the largest contribution to achieving health and environment goals. All our activities work together to get the best results &ndash; lower exposure, lower health risks, and a healthier environment.</p>
