<p><a title="2013 Updated Program Diagram" href="/upload/resources/9/diagram_2013_revised3b_original.pdf">Download a PDF copy of the program diagram here.</a><br /><br />The Trail Area Health &amp; Environment Committee (THEC) oversees the program. THEC is a partnership between the local community, Teck, the Ministry of Environment, and Interior Health. Over the past 20 years of successful collaboration, children&rsquo;s blood levels in Trail have reduced significantly and air quality has greatly improved. THEC&rsquo;s community-led partnership has been recognized internationally as an effective collaborative model for safeguarding health and the environment.&nbsp; In 2011 the program received a <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pGBIt2zZydY">Premier&rsquo;s Innovation and Excellence Award for Partnership</a>.<br /><br /></p>